text: Sara Papadopoulou (born 16 October 1987) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a midfielder for First Division club AC Omonia and the Cyprus women's national team. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers Category:AC Omonia players
